@@ -63,6 +63,8 @@ stable kernels.
 +----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------+
 | ARM            | Cortex-A510     | #1902691        | ARM64_ERRATUM_1902691       |
 +----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------+
+| ARM            | Cortex-A520     | #2966298        | ARM64_ERRATUM_2966298       |
